  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv in short, @tecmusti realized this issue is still there even after injecting a custom client.\r\n\r\nWell, as for default `index`, it works, but when you change using `sortBySelector ` widget, because, `index` is changed to a replica index, the custom client doesn't work (because custom client is set to one `index` ). \r\n\r\nSo a feature like one of these is required\r\n* \"when index is changed, change also the custom client\"\r\n* instantsearch `searchParameters ` should allow `paginationLimitedTo` parameter. ( Details: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/2118#issuecomment-295781597 ) \r\n\r\nI'd prefer the second one which will be less overhaul overall.",
